DCFlight Framework
==================

This repository contains the DCFlight framework, a cross-platform mobile development 
framework built with Dart and Flutter. DCFlight provides a component-based architecture 
for building native mobile applications with a React-like development experience.

Components included in this license:
- DCFlight Core Framework (packages/dcflight)
- DCF Primitives Component Library (packages/dcf_primitives)
- DCFlight CLI Tools (cli)
- Project Templates (packages/template)
- Documentation and Examples

Third-party dependencies may be subject to their own licenses. Please refer to the 
individual package.json, pubspec.yaml, and podspec files for dependency-specific 
license information.

For more information about DCFlight, visit: https://dotcorr.com
